page.title: 14 Housing
page.content:
{Highfield Road
In the area near our school we carried out a house survey. First of all we surveyed the houses in Highfield Road. Most of them were semi-detached with tiles. They had walls of brick and tiles. Some tiles were made of stone and some of the bricks were painted.
{Winchester Road
There are many different houses in Winchester Road. They are detached houses, detached bungalows and semi-detached houses. The numbers on the houses start at 93 and work downwards towards Bodycoates Road. Most of the houses are built of brick.
